cienaWsXcvrMIB.name: cienaWsXcvrMIB

revisions.description: Waveserver Rel 1.2 revised. Major restructuring of this YANG module.

cienaWsXcvrMIB.contactinfo: Web URL: http://www.ciena.com/ Postal: 7035 Ridge Road Hanover, Maryland 21076 U.S.A. Phone: +1 800-921-1144 Fax: +1 410-694-5750
cienaWsXcvrMIB.description: This module defines the common XCVR model. The XCVR is augmented by specific types of transceiver modules if applicable. XCVR objects are permanently available for all ports and reported as empty if the device is not physically present. Attributes read from the device are only available while the device is present.

cwsXcvrXcvrsXcvrIndex.name: cwsXcvrXcvrsXcvrIndex
cwsXcvrXcvrsXcvrIndex.description: XCVR tranceiver index, unique, key value for the XCVR List.

cwsXcvrXcvrIdTable.name: cwsXcvrXcvrIdTable
cwsXcvrXcvrIdTable.description: Identification information of this XCVR instance.

cwsXcvrXcvrIdName.name: cwsXcvrXcvrIdName
cwsXcvrXcvrIdName.description: Name of the XCVR transceiver. Auto generated, and cannot be modified.

cwsXcvrXcvrIdDescription.name: cwsXcvrXcvrIdDescription
cwsXcvrXcvrIdDescription.description: Description of the XCVR. Auto generated, and cannot be modified.

cwsXcvrXcvrStateTable.name: cwsXcvrXcvrStateTable
cwsXcvrXcvrStateTable.description: State information of this XCVR instance.

cwsXcvrXcvrStateAdminState.name: cwsXcvrXcvrStateAdminState
cwsXcvrXcvrStateAdminState.description: Whether Admin State is enabled or disabled for this XCVR's ptp.

cwsXcvrXcvrStateOperationalState.name: cwsXcvrXcvrStateOperationalState
cwsXcvrXcvrStateOperationalState.description: Opertional state of this XCVR, for DCU, it will be empty by default.

cwsXcvrXcvrStatePowerState.name: cwsXcvrXcvrStatePowerState
cwsXcvrXcvrStatePowerState.description: Power State of the XCVR. If it is in low power mode or normal power mode.

cwsXcvrXcvrPropertiesTable.name: cwsXcvrXcvrPropertiesTable
cwsXcvrXcvrPropertiesTable.description: All the Configurable and operational data of this XCVR instance.

cwsXcvrXcvrPropertiesType.name: cwsXcvrXcvrPropertiesType
cwsXcvrXcvrPropertiesType.description: Transceiver type, different transceiver types will have different operational data. Type depends on what is physically plugged in. Read only attribute.

cwsXcvrXcvrPropertiesNumberOfChannels.name: cwsXcvrXcvrPropertiesNumberOfChannels
cwsXcvrXcvrPropertiesNumberOfChannels.description: Number of channels this tranceiver has. Only applicable if a transceiver is plugged in.

cwsXcvrChildPtpIdTable.name: cwsXcvrChildPtpIdTable
cwsXcvrChildPtpIdTable.description: The child ptp this xcvr is associated with.

cwsXcvrChildPtpId.name: cwsXcvrChildPtpId
cwsXcvrChildPtpId.description: The child ptp this xcvr is associated with.

cwsXcvrCienaIdTable.name: cwsXcvrCienaIdTable
cwsXcvrCienaIdTable.description: If the plugged transceiver is a Ciena product, display the Ciena product information. The leafs in this container will be blank if the transceiver is not plugged in or if it is not a Ciena product.

cwsXcvrCienaIdCienaItemNumber.name: cwsXcvrCienaIdCienaItemNumber
cwsXcvrCienaIdCienaItemNumber.description: If the plugged transceiver is a Ciena product, display the product item number. If it is not a Ciena product or if nothing is plugged in, this field will be blank

cwsXcvrCienaIdRevision.name: cwsXcvrCienaIdRevision
cwsXcvrCienaIdRevision.description: If the plugged transceiver is a Ciena product, display the Ciena revision in the format of <prefix>.<number>.<suffix>. If it is not a Ciena product or if nothing is plugged in, this field will be blank

cwsXcvrCienaIdDescription.name: cwsXcvrCienaIdDescription
cwsXcvrCienaIdDescription.description: If the plugged transceiver is a Ciena product, display the Ciena description. If it is not a Ciena product or if nothing is plugged in, this field will be blank

cwsXcvrVendorIdTable.name: cwsXcvrVendorIdTable

cwsXcvrVendorIdName.description: Name of the Vendor that produced this transceiver. For Ciena transceiver, the value will be Ciena.

cwsXcvrVendorIdPartNumber.name: cwsXcvrVendorIdPartNumber
cwsXcvrVendorIdPartNumber.description: Vendor part number of the transceiver.

cwsXcvrVendorIdSerialNumber.name: cwsXcvrVendorIdSerialNumber
cwsXcvrVendorIdSerialNumber.description: Vendor serial number of the XCVR transceiver.
